== PDP-8 from Tom Almy book ==

This project is [https://hackaday.io/project/179357-pdp-8-fpga described here]. It runs on a [http://land-boards.com/blwiki/index.php?title=RETRO-EP4CE15 RETRO-EP4CE15 card] with a [http://land-boards.com/blwiki/index.php?title=QMTECH_EP4CE15_FPGA_Card QMTECH EP4CE15 FPGA card].

Please consider purchasing Tom's book. It's inexpensive ($7) and helpful.

* [https://www.amazon.com/PDP-8-Class-Project-Resoling-Machine-ebook/dp/B07KY5RCJ7/ Amazon link]

